title: Ask HN: Positioning Yourself in the Future of AI: What Should You Build?
text:
As the field of AI continues to advance and grow, developers are increasingly being called upon to build a wide range of applications that can help automate tasks, enhance creativity, and improve search capabilities. With the rise of AI-powered tools and technologies, it's becoming increasingly important for developers to understand how they can position themselves to play a role in this rapidly evolving field.

One question that many developers may be asking is what kinds of AI applications they should be working on to be involved in the future of AI. While some developers may choose to focus on cutting-edge research and development, others may want to explore more practical applications that can be built and used by a wider range of people.

Regardless of the approach that developers take, it's clear that there will be a growing demand for AI-powered tools and technologies in the coming years. As such, developers who are able to build applications that can help automate tasks, enhance creativity, and improve search capabilities will be well-positioned to play a role in the future of AI.

So, to sum up, the question is: What kinds of AI applications should developers be working on to be involved in the future of AI, and how can they position themselves to play a role in this growing field?

(Note Chat-GPT was used to help generate this question and title)

Aks HN: Recover FB account your org owns
text:
Heya, I'm part of a small group in a larger political organization. We had a Facebook page with a lot of content, but the admin went AWOL and we don't have access any longer. I can receive mail at the officially listed email address and snail mail at the officially listed postal address. I also can send requests on offical stationary.

Is there some way to get attention of a human at Meta?

title: Good Calendar for Mxroute?
text:
So I’ve been struggling to get nextcloud via mxroute working with calendars, could be something I’m missing but I keep getting SSL errors when attempting to connect on my iPhone.

So I ask the wider community what calendar (service) do they recommend to compliment mxroute? Ideally something that uses caldav.

Thanks

Ask HN: Are FIFA games being manipulated?
text:
Statistics: What is the probability of unlikely events happening so frequently at roughly the same time? Saudi Arabia wins Argentina, Japan wins Germany, Cameroon wins Brazil, Morocco wins Spain AND Portugal...

As a business, if >60% of my high-income viewers (gen Z + millennials) follow the "woke" ideology, I want to cater to their wants by creating an "underdog" narrative so that I can gain viewership, market share, and loyalty (fans) in this demographic (age & region) to increase my merchandise and ad revenue.
